'''Yindlu yaSatyagraha''', leyi tivekaka ngopfu hi  '''Yindlu yaGandhi''', i muti wa [[Mahatma Gandhi]] lowu akiweke e  [[Joni]], naswona hi laha a tshameke no tirhela kona eka maleme ya 1908 na 1909. Yi tsarisiwe eka nxaxamelo wa matimu an ndhavuko wa Joni. Sweswi SI tirhisiwa tani hi yindlu yo rhurhela va yeni naswona wu thlela wu tirhisiwa tanihi Myuziyamu. Rito '''Satyagraha''' rivula '''kukhona ntiyiso'''. Yindlu leyi yi mpfapfarhutiweriwe Gandi hi Hermann Kallenbach.
